			<h2 class="white">Contribute automatically</h2>
			<p>Sign up once by choosing a monthly amount that works for you. Cancel anytime.<p>
		</div>
		<div class="small-12 xlarge-4 columns" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
			<svg class="icon icon-lend" style="fill: white; color: #63a541;">
